$WmMPID_クワシル,ch00_48_Kvasir_F_Normal,Face|I must perform the ritual, as has
been decided.$k$pI must become Gullveig, and I must
forget all I am to do so.$k$p$Sbs1000|
$WmMPID_クワシル,ch00_48_Kvasir_F_Normal,Face_Pain|I've lost... I can't run any longer...$k$pThis, too...was decided long ago...$k$p

$WmMPID_セイズ,ch00_46_Seith_F_Normal,Face_Anger|If you refuse to change, Kvasir—
if you insist on becoming Gullveig,
then you leave me no choice.$k$pI must put an end to you...to this.$k$p$WmMPID_クワシル,ch00_48_Kvasir_F_Normal,Face_Pain|...$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face_Anger|Seiðr, wait... Killing her now may
put us at risk.$k$p$WmMPID_セイズ,ch00_46_Seith_F_Normal,Face_Anger|Why are you trying to protect her?$k$pIf we do not act now, your world will
be destroyed.$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face_Anger|I think the situation is somewhat
more complex than it may appear.
You have begun to realize, surely.$k$p$WmMPID_セイズ,ch00_46_Seith_F_Normal,Face_Pain|...$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face_Cool|Kvasir lives in the past and becomes
Gullveig in the future, which means...$k$pKvasir must also exist somewhere
in between the past and future,
closer to her becoming Gullveig.$k$pBut we have yet to encounter
a Gullveig or Kvasir from our
own time...$k$p$WmMPID_セイズ,ch00_46_Seith_F_Normal,Face_Pain|When performing the Rite of Light,
I was unable to sense her at all.$k$pNo matter how I searched...I could
not find her. Which means...$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face_Anger|...$k$p$WmMPID_セイズ,ch00_46_Seith_F_Normal,Face_Anger|...Which means...I am her.$k$pKvasir is...me.$k$pAnd I...become Gullveig.$k$p$Sbs150|
